<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">四、我们如何保护您的用户信息</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">五、您</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">六、我们如何处理儿童的个人信息</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">七、您的用户信息如何储存及如何在全球范围转移</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">八、本政策如何更新</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">我们深知用户信息对您的重要性，并会尽全力保护您的用户信息安全可靠。我们致力于维持您对我们的信任，恪守以下原则，保护您的用户信息：权责一致原则、目的明确原则、选择同意原则、最少够用原则、确保安全原则、主体参与原则、公开透明原则等。同时，我们承诺，我们将按业界成熟的安全标准，采取相应的安全保护措施来保护您的用户信息。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">请在使用我们的产品（或服务）前，仔细阅读并了解本隐私政策。</span></p>
<p class="p2" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">一、我们如何收集和使用您的用户信息</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">（一）您使用我司产品或服务过程中我们收集和使用的信息</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">1.</span>当您选择手机号码注册时，如使用一键登陆的功能，基于我们与通信运营商的合作，我们会收集您的<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IMSI</span>，<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">MAC ,</span>网络类型，以便为您提供快捷的登陆服务，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">2.</span>当您选择第三方登陆时，为了满足网络实名制要求，我们会收集您的本机<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">MAC</span>地址，<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">WI-FI</span>信息，粗略位置<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">,SIM</span>卡序列号，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">3.</span>当您使用留言功能时，为了满足网络实名制要求，我们会获取设备识别码（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Mac</span>地址<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">/APNS Token/IME),IP</span>地址，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">4.</span>当您使用内容发布、内容推送功能时；为了满足网络实名制要求，我们会获取网络信息包括：<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IP</span>地址，<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">WI-FI</span>信息，基站信息相关信息，设备识别码（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Mac</span>地址<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">/APNS Token/IME)</span>，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">5.</span>当您使用相机功能时会请求您的相机、照片、麦克风权限，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">6.</span>我们的产品集成神策<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">SDK,</span>需要收集您的设备<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Mac</span>地址、唯一设备识别码（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IMEI/MAC/SIM</span>卡<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IMSI</span>信息）已提供统计分析服务，并通过地理位置校准数据准确性，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">7.</span>我们可能会使用极光<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">SDK</span>来为你推送消息通知，极光会请求您的设备信息（设备平台，设备厂商，设备识别码<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IMEI</span>、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IMSI</span>、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">MAC</span>、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IDFA</span>）已安装应用列表信息、网络信息（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IP</span>地址、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">WIFI</span>信息），给您提供更好的推送服务和体验，如果您拒绝授权提供，将无法使用该附加功能，但不会影响您正常使用嗨刻网的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">8.</span>图片下载、分享功能；您注册成为嗨刻用户后，通过嗨刻下载、保存分享图片时，我们会请求您的<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">mac</span>地址，访问外部储存卡，当前链接<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">wifi</span>信息、存储权限，如拒绝提供您将无法使用保存分享图片功能；在您同意隐私协议后，我们还会自动收集您的已安装列表应用信息，以便在您使用注册、登陆和分享功能时判断您可以使用哪些第三方平台登陆和分享。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">我们仅会出于本政策所述的业务功能，收集和使用您的用户信息，收集用户信息的目的在于向您提供产品或服务，您有权自行选择是否提供该信息，但多数情况下，如果您不提供，我们可能无法向您提供相应的服务，也无法回应您遇到的问题：</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您注册、登录嗨刻时，我们会收集您的请求申请您的设备信息权限，手机号码、短信验证码。您可以在验证已有的手机号码后，随时修改绑定的登录手机号码。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">若您以其他方式关联登录嗨刻，我们可能从相关方获取您授权共享的账户信息，并在您同意本政策后将您的相关方账号与您的嗨刻账号绑定，使您可以通过该账号直接登录并使用嗨刻：（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">1</span>）当您使用微博账号登录时，我们会收集您的微博账号昵称、头像、简介、性别、生日公开信息，以及绑定的手机号码；（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">2</span>）当您使用微信登录时，我们只会收集您的性别信息；以及绑定的手机号码；（<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">3</span>）当您使用<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Apple&nbsp;ID</span>登录时，我们会获取您<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Apple&nbsp;ID</span>的电子邮箱地址。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您通过做任务获取积分时，我们也会记录您的任务进度和积分数量。如您使用积分兑换领取时，并在满足一定条件后申请提现，您需要绑定您的微信账号。如您拒绝绑定微信账号，您可能无法进行零钱提现。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">&ldquo;</span>关注<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">&rdquo;</span>中使用查看好友功能时，我们将收集您的通讯录信息，以便为您推荐您通讯录中使用嗨刻的联系人。如果您拒绝提供这些信息，您将无法使用此项功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您使用我们提供的搜索服务时，我们会收集您搜索的关键字信息、搜索历史记录、设备信息。为了提供高效的搜索服务，部分信息会暂时存储在您的本地设备中。在此，您需要注意的是，单独的搜索关键字信息无法识别您的个人身份，其不属于您的个人信息，因此我们有权以其他的目的对其进行使用；只有当您的搜索关键字信息与您的其他信息互有联系并可以结合识别您的个人身份时，我们会将您的搜索关键字信息作为您的个人信息，与您的搜索历史记录一同按照本政策进行处理与保护。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您使用设置功能编辑资料时，向您申请授权相机、照片的储存权限，您可以根据意愿进一步完善您的档案资料，包括修改头像、昵称、性别，设置简介、填写生日、城市和学校。如果您拒绝提供这些信息，不会影响您使用嗨刻的基本功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">在您使用意见反馈功能时我们向您申请存储权限；除了给我们提出宝贵的意见（包括意见截屏）外，您可以选择留下您的<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">QQ</span>号或微信以便我们与您联系。如果您拒绝提供这些联系信息，也不会影响您向我们反馈意见或使用嗨刻的其他功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">使用发布功能发布动态时需要添加地理位置，届时我们会申请获取标记您发布内容的地理位置时，如果您拒绝提供该信息，您将无法使用此功能。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">我们如在上述场景之外获得您的个人信息，将重新征得您的明示同意，并在获得您明示同意前向您充分说明应用场景与获取您相关信息的内容与范围。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">我们将会依据与上述相关应用的运营方的约定、对个人信息来源的合法性进行确认后，在符合相关法律法规规定的前提下，使用您的上述个人信息。<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">&nbsp;ID</span>登录时，我们会获取您<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">Apple&nbsp;ID</span>的电子邮箱地址。收集这些信息是为了帮您创建嗨刻账号，如果您拒绝提供这些信息，将影响您注册使用嗨刻。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">向您提供服务图片内容的浏览以及展示内容和推送功能（核心功能）。图片、文章内容的浏览是嗨刻网的核心功能，为此我们需要向您收集如下个人信息。当您通过嗨刻网进行图片、文章内容的浏览时，嗨刻网系统会自动接受并记录您使用嗨刻网时的设备信息（如设备型号、操作系统、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IP</span>地址软硬件信息）。如果您拒绝同意我们的收集，则我们将无法向您提供内容的浏览功能。我们还可能收集您的浏览器类型，以此来为您提供信息展示的最优方案。</span></p>
<p class="p1" style="margin: 0px 0px 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: \'PingFang SC\';"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">展示内容和推送功能同样是嗨刻网的核心功能，为了向您提供更切合您需求的页面、图片、文章内容，我们需要向您收集有关网络日志（包括您输入的搜索关键词和点击链接；您浏览过的内容；访问的日期和时间；及您请求的网页记录、操作系统、软件版本号、<span class="s1" style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">IP</span>地址）。在此过程中，我们收集您的浏览记录，浏览记录包括您浏览的图片、文章，您可以通过推送展示的内容及图片选择关闭，关闭按钮会在内容及图片的右上角处显示。</span></p>
